videos.headline: Duke TE bobbles it and holds on for TD
videos.description: Duke tight end Noah Gray bobbles the ball then hauls it in for the 25-yard TD.

videos.headline: VT WR grabs the 27-yard TD
videos.description: Virginia Tech WR Damon Hazelton hauls in the 27-yard TD to give the Hokies the 10-7 lead.

videos.headline: VT TE does it all on his way to 67-yard TD
videos.description: VT tight end Dalton Keene grabs the short pass, breaks multiple tackles and is able to score the 67-yard TD.

videos.headline: Peoples powers his way in for Virginia Tech TD
videos.description: Virginia Tech running back Steven Peoples carries tacklers to the end zone for the 6-yard rushing TD.

videos.headline: Duke RB leaps over pile for TD
videos.description: Duke running back Deon Jackson dives over the pile for a 1-yard rushing touchdown.
